---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
const title = 'Support — Bankrolly';
const description = 'Get help with Bankrolly. Manage your subscription, restore purchases, delete your account, or contact support.';
---
<Base title={title} description={description}>
  <section>
    <article class="prose">
      <h1>Bankrolly Support</h1>
      <p class="updated">Last updated: June 11, 2026</p>

      <p>We're happy to help with any questions about Bankrolly.</p>

      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@bankrolly.online">support@bankrolly.online</a></p>
      <p>We typically respond within 1–2 business days. Please include your device model and iOS version so we can help you faster.</p>

      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

      <h3>How do I manage or cancel my subscription?</h3>
      <p>Subscriptions are billed through your Apple ID. To manage or cancel:</p>
      <ol>
        <li>Open <strong>Settings</strong> on your iPhone or iPad</li>
        <li>Tap your name → <strong>Subscriptions</strong></li>
        <li>Select <strong>Bankrolly Pro</strong> and choose your plan or tap <strong>Cancel Subscription</strong></li>
      </ol>
      <p>You can also open <strong>Settings → Manage subscription</strong> inside the app.</p>

      <h3>I purchased Pro but features are still locked</h3>
      <p>Open the paywall in the app and tap <strong>Restore purchases</strong>. Make sure you are signed in with the same Apple ID that made the purchase. If it still doesn't unlock, email us and we'll fix it.</p>

      <h3>How do I delete my account?</h3>
      <p>Open <strong>Settings</strong> in the app and tap <strong>Delete account</strong>. This permanently removes your account and all associated data. You can also email us to request deletion.</p>

      <h3>How do I sign in?</h3>
      <p>Bankrolly supports Sign in with Apple, Google, or email and password. If you have trouble signing in, try again in a few minutes or contact us.</p>

      <h3>Is Bankrolly a gambling app?</h3>
      <p>No. Bankrolly is a bankroll and session <strong>tracking</strong> tool for informational and analytical purposes only. It does not provide gambling services or facilitate real-money betting.</p>

      <h2>Legal</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a></li>
        <li><a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a></li>
      </ul>
    </article>
  </section>
</Base>
